@q *** (3) command --> BEGINFIG LEFT_PARENTHESIS @>
@q *** (3) numeric_expression RIGHT_PARENTHESIS. @> 

@*2 \§command> $\longrightarrow$ 
\.{BEGINFIG} \.{LEFT\_PARENTHESIS}' \§numeric expression> 
\.{RIGHT\_PARENTHESIS}.

\LOG
\initials{LDF 2004.06.19.}  
